# Style-preferences memory lives here.
#
# Tracks how the student prefers to learn — observed, not just declared.
#
# Files:
#   profile.md       — stated preferences from onboarding
#   observed.md      — patterns the agent has inferred (retention by format,
#                      time-of-day performance, session length sweet spot,
#                      engagement triggers)
#   corrections.md   — explicit overrides ("don't use cooking analogies",
#                      "I learn better with code than prose")
#
# Observed preferences update after every session via adapt-style skill.
